===Etymology===
Via {{etyl|fr}} {{term|koumis|lang=fr}}, {{etyl|de}} {{term|Kumiss|lang=de}}, from {{etyl|ru}} {{term|кумыс|tr=kumýs|lang=ru}}, borrowed from a {{etyl|trk}} source. Compare Tatar {{term|кымыз|lang=tt|tr=kymyz}}, Kazakh {{term|қымыз|tr=qımız}}, Turkish {{term|kımız|lang=tr}}.

